WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:03.535
    Adrian has been talking
    to the police about us.

00:03.604 --> 00:07.339
I don't think Deran is strong
enough to handle this.

00:07.408 --> 00:09.407
      So what's the plan?
           Indonesia?

00:09.476 --> 00:11.610
         Great surfing,
     no extradition treaty.

00:11.678 --> 00:13.612
       Her name is Gia --
           the fence.

00:13.680 --> 00:15.880
       I'll let her know
      you're coming today.

00:15.950 --> 00:17.549
      I have a job for us.

00:17.618 --> 00:20.752
   It's quick, nothing fancy,
           big score.

00:20.821 --> 00:21.886
           Hey, Jed.

00:21.888 --> 00:22.887
          [ Gunshot ]

00:22.957 --> 00:25.557
        Come out, boys!
         Let's do this!

00:25.626 --> 00:27.225
          [ Gunshots ]

00:27.294 --> 00:28.293
             Smurf!

00:28.362 --> 00:29.361
       Shoot me, Andrew.

00:29.430 --> 00:30.362
              No.

00:30.431 --> 00:31.830
       I'm already dead!

00:31.898 --> 00:33.498
    She's gonna do it, Pope!

00:33.500 --> 00:34.899
        -Smurf! Christ!
      -She's gonna do it!

00:34.969 --> 00:36.368
            -Smurf!
       -Pull the trigger!

00:36.436 --> 00:38.637
          [ Gunshot ]

00:38.705 --> 00:41.239
   Why don't you and me just
   have ourselves some fun...

00:41.308 --> 00:43.175
             -Ugh!
              -No!

00:43.243 --> 00:45.109
          [ Grunting ]

00:45.111 --> 00:46.578
     Jed, leave her alone!

00:46.647 --> 00:47.780
          [ Grunting ]

00:47.848 --> 00:49.714
              Aah!

00:49.716 --> 00:52.250
        [ Baby crying ]

00:52.319 --> 00:54.386
        Have you decided
     what to name them yet?

00:54.455 --> 00:58.390
     Julia. But this one...
      Colin liked Andrew.

00:59.660 --> 01:03.261
               ♪♪

01:03.330 --> 01:08.600
     ♪ She stares deeply

01:08.669 --> 01:12.737
      ♪ Locked inside me

01:12.807 --> 01:15.808
      ♪ Burnin' brightly

01:15.876 --> 01:19.077
