02:29.416 --> 02:31.550
       Where'd he put it?

02:31.618 --> 02:33.752
    I brought you breakfast.

02:33.820 --> 02:37.356
        I'm not hungry.

02:39.894 --> 02:42.026
      You can always come
   and eat with us, you know?

02:42.028 --> 02:44.296
         I wanna leave.

